00:45:03.390 --> 00:45:06.960
When I coach somebody, I can--

00:45:06.960 --> 00:45:09.330
all of us, we're getting
more and more skilled at it--

00:45:09.330 --> 00:45:14.010
you can smell the exact
which one of these 16 flavors

00:45:14.010 --> 00:45:14.965
is happening.

00:45:14.965 --> 00:45:16.590
So let's just move
on to the last piece

00:45:16.590 --> 00:45:18.390
of this, which is
the way all of this

00:45:18.390 --> 00:45:21.690
becomes really,
really helpful is,

00:45:21.690 --> 00:45:26.100
we have a project going called
the Radical Brilliance project.

00:45:26.100 --> 00:45:28.920
And we are able, because
more and more people

00:45:28.920 --> 00:45:34.170
are involved in this now, we're
able to actually map practice.

00:45:34.170 --> 00:45:38.400
Now, what I mean by
practice is anything,

00:45:38.400 --> 00:45:42.450
anything that's ever been done
by anybody in the whole history

00:45:42.450 --> 00:45:45.990
of humanity which changes
your state of consciousness.

00:45:45.990 --> 00:45:48.600
Anything which has
the effect of shifting

00:45:48.600 --> 00:45:51.510
your state of consciousness,
we would call a practice.

00:45:51.510 --> 00:45:54.390
So meditation is
obviously a practice,

00:45:54.390 --> 00:45:59.370
but so is going shopping,
if it changes your state.

00:45:59.370 --> 00:46:00.630
So is going swimming.

00:46:00.630 --> 00:46:01.560
So is making love.

00:46:01.560 --> 00:46:04.440
So is having a glass of wine.

00:46:04.440 --> 00:46:07.800
Under the right circumstances,
anything could be a practice.

00:46:07.800 --> 00:46:12.780
But what we see now, as
the more this cycle becomes

00:46:12.780 --> 00:46:16.380
accurate and verifiable
in experience,

00:46:16.380 --> 00:46:19.920
we realize anything that
any human being has ever

00:46:19.920 --> 00:46:23.070
done in the history
of all of humanity,

00:46:23.070 --> 00:46:24.840
anything we have
ever done that was

00:46:24.840 --> 00:46:29.850
intended to change consciousness
fits somewhere into this cycle.

00:46:29.850 --> 00:46:32.330
So any consciousness-changing
practice

00:46:32.330 --> 00:46:35.030
is actually a
viable way of moving

00:46:35.030 --> 00:46:37.250
through a part of the
cycle where you're blocked.

