Setting intentions--
there used to be

00:47:15.927 --> 00:47:18.260
this thing about the law of
attraction was very popular.

00:47:18.260 --> 00:47:21.260
Setting an intention-- I'm
going to do that in the future.

00:47:21.260 --> 00:47:22.970
That happens right after 3:00.

00:47:22.970 --> 00:47:25.040
It's got all of
the flavor of flow,

00:47:25.040 --> 00:47:27.680
but it's got the
future attached to it.

